on across healthy and pathological ageing, and it will be of great interest to advanced undergraduates, postgraduates and researchers in psychology and related subject areas concerned with the effects of human ageing, including several areas of medicine"--cProvided by publisher.  a43 0aMemoryxAge factors. 0aShort-term memory. 0aCognitionxAge factors. 0aAgingxPsychological aspects.1 aLogie, Robert H.,eeditor of compilation.1 aMorris, Robin,d1958-eeditor of compilation. 0aCurrent issues in memory.  aBF 378 A33 W67 2015c1hUAHS-Bi0162035193000  aBF 378 A33 W67 2015wLCc1i0162035193000lON_SHELFmUAHSSp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu11/26/201401ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n93802361bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/84867195